# Page & Layout Conventions

## Page Structure
- Pages under `src/app/[locale]/` — never create pages at root `src/app/`
- Each section has `page.tsx` (content) and `layout.tsx` (metadata via `buildPageMetadata`)
- `generateStaticParams` must return `[{ locale: "en" }, { locale: "es" }]`

## Metadata
- Use `buildPageMetadata()` from `src/lib/seo.ts` in `layout.tsx` files
- Always provide both `en` and `es` translations in dictionaries before referencing them

## Client Pages
- Use `"use client"` for interactive pages
- Access locale via `useParams()` or `useLocale()` from i18n provider
- Gate AI features behind `useRequireAuth()`
- Avoid `window.scrollTo` — keep scroll management within container refs

## Error Handling
- Each locale group has `error.tsx` and `not-found.tsx`
- API failures should show user-friendly messages, not raw errors
